<h3>Pairing statistics with footnotes</h3>

<p>Include a footnote on the same page if you're making a claim, especially if the statistic comes from an external source. This can increase the credibility of the statistic and can better integrate the data with the page content.</p>
{% call components.example(palette='light') %}
